---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Our Teams - The Kumlawdi Foundation" description="Meet Lady Yakpak and Tampa Flex, the football teams that form the foundation of The Kumlawdi Foundation community.">
  <div class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-light to-white py-16 lg:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-6 font-inter">
            Our Teams
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
            Our football teams serve as the starting point of our community, bringing together athletes who share a passion for excellence both on and off the field.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Teams Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
          <!-- Lady Yakpak -->
          <div class="bg-brand-light p-8 rounded-lg">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4 font-inter">Lady YakPak</h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-secondary mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">Girls Flag Football Team</p>
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">
              YAKPAK – Young And Knowledgeable Positive And Kind
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
              YAKPAK is more than a team—it's a culture, a sisterhood, and a movement. Built on the principles of empowerment, discipline, and unity, YAKPAK represents a generation of young women who refuse to settle for average. These athletes train with purpose, lead with confidence, and uplift each other every step of the way.
            </p>
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
              YAKPAK embodies the belief that greatness begins with mindset. Our girls commit to working hard, staying accountable, and pushing past limits—on the field, in the classroom, and in life. Every practice, every rep, and every challenge becomes an opportunity to grow stronger, smarter, and more resilient.
            </p>
            <p class="text-brand-gray italic font-semibold">
              YAKPAK is not just who we are. It's how we walk, how we work, and how we win.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-brand-gray">
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray">
                <strong>Follow us:</strong> <a href="https://instagram.com/yakpakflagfb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-secondary hover:underline">@yakpakflagfb</a><br>
                <strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="tel:8132609518" class="text-brand-secondary hover:underline">813-260-9518</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Tampa Flex -->
          <div class="bg-brand-light p-8 rounded-lg">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4 font-inter">Tampa Flex</h2>
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-secondary mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider">Boys 7v7 Football Team</p>
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">
              FLEX – Focus. Leadership. Effort. eXcellence.
            </p>
            <div class="mb-6">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-primary mb-2">Meaning Breakdown:</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-brand-gray text-sm">
                <li>• <strong>Focus:</strong> Stay committed to goals on and off the field.</li>
                <li>• <strong>Leadership:</strong> Inspire teammates through attitude and action.</li>
                <li>• <strong>Effort:</strong> Always give your best, no matter the challenge.</li>
                <li>• <strong>eXcellence:</strong> Strive for improvement every day—in sports, school, and life.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <p class="text-brand-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
              FLEX reinforces the core values of youth athletics while keeping the message energetic and easy for kids to remember. Tampa Flex brings together dedicated athletes committed to excellence in football and personal growth. The team serves as a cornerstone of our community, fostering connections and opportunities for development.
            </p>
            <p class="text-brand-gray">
              Tampa Flex players benefit from comprehensive support including training resources, travel opportunities for tournaments, and access to mentorship and academic programs that prepare them for success beyond athletics.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-brand-gray">
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-gray">
                <strong>Follow us:</strong> <a href="https://instagram.com/tampaflex7v7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-secondary hover:underline">@tampaflex7v7</a><br>
                <strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="tel:8134011424" class="text-brand-secondary hover:underline">813-401-1424</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Team Support Section -->
        <div class="bg-white border-t border-brand-gray pt-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-8 text-center font-inter">Supporting Our Teams</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-secondary mb-2">Equipment</div>
              <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Uniforms, headgear, cleats, and game-day essentials</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-secondary mb-2">Travel</div>
              <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Tournament and away game support</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-secondary mb-2">Training</div>
              <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Weekly WR training and skill development</p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-secondary mb-2">Scholarships</div>
              <p class="text-brand-gray text-sm">Academic and athletic opportunities</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Community Impact -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-brand-light">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4 font-inter">More Than a Team</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-brand-gray leading-relaxed">
            Our teams are more than just football—they're communities of support, growth, and opportunity. Through shared experiences on and off the field, athletes build lasting relationships and develop skills that serve them throughout their lives. We create pathways to success, helping students become leaders, scholars, and role models in their communities.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-brand-secondary text-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 font-inter">Support Our Teams</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-8 opacity-90">
          Your sponsorship helps provide equipment, travel support, training resources, and scholarship opportunities for our athletes.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}support`} class="btn-outline inline-block text-center">
            Become a Sponsor
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/donation-form/sponsorship-proposal-package" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-white text-brand-secondary px-6 py-3 rounded font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors inline-block text-center">
            Donate Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
